{"type":"message","id":"5af6cd76","parentId":"2f16a9c6","timestamp":"2026-04-05T02:33:05.990Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"      Jetzt lass mich eine Zusammenfassung erstellen:","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"  ## ✅ Integration Abgeschlossen!\n\n### 📁 Struktur\n\n```\npackages/resilient-agent/\n├── src/resilient_agent/\n│   ├── __init__.py          # Package-Exports\n│   ├── agent.py             # ResilientAgent Hauptklasse\n│   ├── model_router.py      # Task-basierte Modellauswahl\n│   ├── timeout_middleware.py # 3-Tier-Timeout-Handling\n│   └── timeout_config.py    # Modellspezifische Timeouts\n├── tests/\n│   ├── __init__.py\n│   └── test_resilient_agent.py\n├── pyproject.toml           # Package-Konfiguration\n└── README.md\n```\n\n### 🔧 OpenClaw Config Erweitert\n\nIn `openclaw.json` hinzugefügt:\n- **Timeouts**: `timeoutSeconds: 900`, `idleTimeoutSeconds: 120`, `stallTimeoutSeconds: 45`\n- **Fallbacks**: `kimi-coding/k2p5` → `kimi-coding/kimi-k2-thinking`\n- **Failover**: Automatisch bei `rate_limit`, `timeout`, `stall`, etc.\n\n### 🧪 Tests\n\n18 Unit Tests für:\n- Timeout-Profile\n- Model Router\n- Middleware (Success, Timeouts, Retry)\n- Resilient Agent\n\n---\n\n**Soll ich:**\n1. Tests ausführen?\n2. Beispiel-Skript erstellen?\n3. Gateway neustarten für neue Config?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":83769,"output":333,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84102,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775356369148}}
