{"type":"message","id":"d9b4a161","parentId":"3a912b18","timestamp":"2026-04-05T03:27:52.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" Perfect! I've added the new section \"Always Say When Done (CRITICAL)\" to AGENTS.md. Now let me confirm completion with the user.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"     ✅ **Fertig!**\n\nIch habe den neuen Arbeitsstandard dokumentiert:\n\n## Neue Regel in AGENTS.md:\n\n### \"Always Say When Done (CRITICAL)\"\n\n```\n✅ \"Fertig!\" (kurz, wenn alles erledigt)\n✅ \"Fertig! Noch Fragen zu X?\" (wenn Fragen offen)\n❌ Einfach aufhören zu antworten\n```\n\n**Das gilt jetzt für ALLE zukünftigen Sessions!** 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":2758,"output":142,"cacheRead":131776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134676,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775359664074}}
